1
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,039
Yufeng,

2
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,210
congratulations to you and Fu Fan.

3
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,680
Thank you.

4
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,330
I'll treat you to Zhajiangmian later.

5
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:51,580
Why Zhajiangmian?

6
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:53,160
Because Fu Fan and I

7
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,850
didn't have a ceremony.

8
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:58,280
We just put our beddings together,

9
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,560
and that was it.

10
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:02,780
But the kitchen staff didn't agree that day.

11
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:03,800
They told me,

12
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:07,200
since we didn't get to drink wedding wine,

13
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:09,000
or eat wedding candies,

14
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:11,520
we should at least have a bowl of Zhajiangmian.

15
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,360
I said okay.

16
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:16,100
Army Commander Chen had the same standard for his wedding.

17
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:17,520
I've heard for a long time

18
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:20,250
that the Communist Party's style is very frugal,

19
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,600
and it's really true.

20
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Eating Zhajiangmian for a wedding.

21
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:27,130
Actually, I have been married before.

22
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:29,400
My ex-husband was Jiang Zhen.

23
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,970
The enemy threw his body

24
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:36,200
into a river like this one.

25
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,300
We looked for several days

26
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,050
before we found him.

27
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:43,640
I buried him myself at the foot of Maoshan.

28
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,400
At that time, we had been married

29
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,930
for less than three months.

30
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,360
It was like a dream.

31
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:54,280
Later, I met Xie.

32
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,400
Everyone said a cadre came from Yan'an,

33
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,400
and dragged me to have a look.

34
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,760
He was riding a horse.

35
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,160
His uniform was washed pale,

36
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,480
the collar buttoned tightly,

37
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,000
and a gun tucked in his waist.

38
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,330
Most importantly, his puttees

39
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,120
were tied neatly.

40
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,000
That was what the Red Army looked like in my heart.

41
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,400
Commander Xie really has a great temperament.

42
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,520
He is tall and mighty,

43
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,880
yet gentle and elegant.

44
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:23,160
He wasn't like this when he was courting me.

45
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,040
What was he like?

46
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,280
At the very beginning,

47
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,760
I still had some concerns in my heart.

48
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:30,690
What do you mean?

49
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:35,200
Because I had been married before.

50
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,400
Before me, Fu Fan

51
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,120
also had an

52
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,130
unforgettable relationship.

53
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:47,720
At that time,

54
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,920
I felt I had betrayed Jiang Zhen.

55
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,980
I couldn't accept myself.

56
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,970
Actually, I was quite selfish.

57
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,970
I didn't dare to accept Xie's love,

58
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,329
nor did I dare to lose it.

59
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,840
Xie said I was torturing myself,

60
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,970
and also torturing him.

61
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,360
He told me.

62
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,480
He was married before.

63
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:09,320
She was a revolutionary comrade introduced by the organization.

64
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,200
However,

65
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,520
during the KMT's encirclement,

66
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,120
she sacrificed herself.

67
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,519
My last marriage,

68
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,519
was during the time of the Red Fourteenth Army,

69
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,279
introduced to me by the organization.

70
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,480
Later,

71
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:25,140
we encountered the KMT's encirclement.

72
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,400
I then

73
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,960
followed the central column north.

74
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,160
She was a confidential traffic officer,

75
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,480
so she had a mission

76
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,560
and stayed in the Soviet area,

77
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,840
fighting guerrillas with Army Commander Chen.

78
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,680
After arriving in Yan'an,

79
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,120
I found out

80
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,720
that while delivering salt to

81
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,760
the guerrillas trapped in the mountains,

82
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,320
on her way,

83
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,130
she was killed by the enemy.

84
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,980
I was so sad at the time,

85
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,680
I couldn't get over it for years.

86
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,700
Ten years of life and death, both boundless.

87
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,520
Without thinking, it is unforgettable.

88
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,560
I even said to myself,

89
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,560
Forget it.

90
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,320
This life is fine like this.

91
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:04,760
Yufeng,

92
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,360
you are an open-minded person.

93
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,800
I think he is open and aboveboard.

94
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,930
I really admire him.

95
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,840
Although emotionally

96
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,570
we are not a blank slate.

97
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,480
But I believe

98
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,560
we can still be sincere.

99
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,240
And profound.

100
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,720
Fu Fan.

101
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,490
I really admire you.

102
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,920
You are so brave.

103
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,720
You can be too.

104
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:32,000
Come, give me a hand.

105
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,480
Amidst war and exile,

106
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:24,520
surviving has become the greatest fortune.

107
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,880
So,

108
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:28,380
we have to live up to this fortune.

109
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:29,280
Yunkui,

110
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,720
use this waterweed to brush it first.

111
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,680
Don't dirty the water.

112
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,360
Okay.

113
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,440
But I think,

114
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,040
if we live, we must live well.

115
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,240
Yunkui,

116
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,080
I want to ask you a question.

117
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:49,960
What do you think we are fighting

118
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:53,000
bloody battles for?

119
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:57,040
Hatred. Hatred for the Japanese.

120
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,800
I completely agree.

121
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,280
But I think

122
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,760
it might not just be that.

123
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:07,600
We have experienced so much suffering.

124
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,280
Even in the most desperate

125
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,540
and depressing times,

126
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:15,240
it is still hope that sustains us.

127
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,440
It can become

128
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,840
our strong backing.

129
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,320
Yufeng,

130
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:26,080
you really are a poet.

131
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,320
A romantic poet.

132
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,520
Stop joking.

133
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,760
Me, a poet?

134
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:31,040
I don't deserve that.

135
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,240
But then again,

136
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:34,360
if you talk about our troops,

137
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:37,360
the greatest poet is Army Commander Chen.

138
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,880
He has a poem 'Three Poems from Meiling'.

139
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:41,159
Have you read it?

140
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,960
I think this poem

141
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,120
exactly answers

142
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,720
the question we just discussed.

143
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:53,640
What exactly are we fighting for?

144
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:58,600
What if I am beheaded today?

145
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:02,160
Hardships of starting anew mean many battles.

146
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:05,170
Going to the underworld to gather old troops.

147
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:09,200
A hundred thousand banners will slay Yama.

148
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:13,140
The beacon fires in the south have burned for ten years.

149
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,920
This head must be hung at the nation's gate.

150
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,560
Those who survive must work hard.

151
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:22,000
Let news of victory fly in as paper money.

152
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:25,650
Joining the revolution means making it home.

153
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:28,760
The reign of terror must have an end.

154
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:32,039
Dying for a just cause is a matter for today.

155
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:36,760
Freedom flowers will be planted all over the world.

156
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:49,640
I got you a new pair of glasses.

157
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,320
See if they fit.

158
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,530
Come on, try them on.

159
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:54,840
Try them.

160
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,360
Let's see.

161
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,860
You should be able to see clearly now.

162
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:12,120
Why can't I still see clearly?

163
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,360
This...

164
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,220
It's not clear?

165
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,840
Then look at these big words.

166
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,560
Look at this character.

167
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:22,480
Is it the character Shen?

168
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,240
No.

169
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:26,960
What's going on?

170
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,320
Why can't I even see

171
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,560
such big words clearly?

172
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,520
What's happening?

173
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,560
What's going on?

174
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:33,920
Where did you get these?

175
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,380
It shouldn't be like this.

176
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:38,000
It's a top optical shop in Shanghai.

177
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,660
Then I'll go get them changed.

178
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:40,920
Let's go change them.

179
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,400
Wanfu.

180
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:48,160
I taught you the "Thousand Character Classic",

181
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:50,080
and you know so many characters now.

182
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:53,080
From now on, you'll read the newspaper to me.

183
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:54,840
Okay, I'll read it to you.

184
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,200
The Japanese Northern Area Army,

185
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:04,880
led by Lieutenant General Hayao Tada,

186
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,400
swiftly broke through enemy lines.

187
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:12,040
The Chinese defenders at Zhongtiao Mountains

188
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,960
retreated across the board.

189
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:17,200
Total casualties exceeded

190
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:18,680
100,000.

191
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,240
Retreated across the board?

192
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,200
Casualties exceeded 100,000?

193
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,280
Master!

194
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:25,840
Dad!

195
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:26,600
What kind of battle situation is this?

196
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,000
Sit down first.

197
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,680
Don't get angry. Please don't get mad.

198
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,480
Don't get mad.

199
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,920
Losing every battle.

200
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,720
Has our nation's fortune

201
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,920
declined to this extent?

202
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,920
Heaven is no longer protecting China.

203
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:44,440
Dad, the doctor said

204
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,720
you can't get angry.

205
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,960
Don't get angry.

206
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:47,800
Keep reading.

207
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,760
Hurry up and keep reading.

208
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,560
I...

209
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,880
Keep reading, quick.

210
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,360
Read it.

211
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,600
Quick.

212
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,680
I'll read.

213
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,040
Don't read it.

214
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:03,680
Read it.

215
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:06,400
Master, look.

216
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,280
This is a newspaper run by the Japanese.

217
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,560
Look at what's written.

218
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,320
Would they say anything good about us?

219
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,840
The date is wrong too.

220
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,880
Who brought this old newspaper?

221
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,000
It must be Yueming.

222
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,860
Old newspaper?

223
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,760
He loves going through newspapers.

224
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,400
Let me find today's paper.

225
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,250
Last month's paper.

226
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,120
Here it is.

227
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,200
Here.

228
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,560
Master, look.

229
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,280
This is the new one.

230
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:32,210
This is yesterday's paper.

231
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,520
Read it to me quickly.

232
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:36,360
I'll read the new battle report to you.

233
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,760
I'll read the new report.

234
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:49,200
Victory in the Battle of Changsha.

235
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:52,000
Victory in the Battle of Changsha.

236
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:52,720
Changsha.

237
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,120
Changsha.

238
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,400
Read it.

239
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,440
Read it.

240
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:04,440
Our Changsha defenders took the initiative to attack.

241
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:09,440
The Japanese Army collapsed at the first encounter.

242
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:14,600
Our defenders split into two groups

243
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:17,080
to surround the Japanese Army.

244
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:19,280
And the Japanese Army

245
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:21,560
fled to...

246
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,520
The river where Qu Yuan drowned himself...

247
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:24,400
What was its name?

248
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:25,280
Miluo River.

249
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:25,720
Right.

250
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,960
It says they fled to the Miluo River.

251
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,520
Come, let me see.

252
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,520
Don't look at it.

253
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,360
Just let Wanfu read it to you, Father.

254
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,720
Let me see.

255
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,800
Yujiao, is that really what it says?

256
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,170
Why can't I see clearly?

257
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:43,960
That's exactly what is written here.

258
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:48,760
Master, look.

259
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:55,600
The Japanese Army fled to the Miluo River,

260
00:12:59,560 --> 00:13:00,120
north.

261
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:01,320
North.

262
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,880
North of the Miluo River.

263
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:05,480
That's truly wonderful.

264
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,600
This is exactly...

265
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:11,160
'Truly brave and martial,

266
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:14,680
Strong and invincible to the end.'

267
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,600
Good.

268
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:20,840
Master, you startled me.

269
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,380
Once you started quoting poetry,

270
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,160
I finally felt relieved.

271
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:28,120
Father, are you hungry?

272
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,600
Yes, I want some porridge.

273
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:32,680
I'll make it for you.

274
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:34,000
Good.

275
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:36,160
I'll go help.

276
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:45,160
North of the Miluo River.

277
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:48,360
Yes.

278
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,800
North of the Miluo River.

279
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:56,040
Good.

280
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:57,920
Great.

281
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,920
You just blurted out Changsha.

282
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:02,240
The situation in Changsha is tense right now.

283
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:04,700
Whenever I get nervous, I think of Changsha.

284
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:05,440
Besides,

285
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,740
what if a war really breaks out later?

286
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:09,960
And what if we actually win?

287
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:12,680
No.

288
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,360
What do we do from now on?

289
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:16,220
Since we started lying today,

290
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:18,330
do we have to keep making things up?

291
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,320
But

292
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,200
I don't think there's anything right now

293
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:25,530
more effective than the news of a victory.

294
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:26,680
Didn't you see Master?

295
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:28,160
As soon as he heard the news of victory,

296
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:30,090
his blood clots seemed to clear up.

297
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,400
It just so happens

298
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,890
Father's eyesight is poor.

299
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:44,880
I really don't know

300
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:47,210
whether this is a good thing or a bad thing.

301
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:50,100
We can't think that far ahead.

302
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:52,320
Whatever medicine works now,

303
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,400
we will take it.

304
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:04,880
I'm returning to Haiwen this week.

305
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:06,760
As for me,

306
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,280
I want to ask you

307
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:13,680
if you are willing to work with me in Haiwen.

308
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,200
I've asked.

309
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:20,200
Female comrades can't join the combat troops,

310
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:22,000
but there are actually many other jobs

311
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,120
you can do in the regiment.

312
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,640
Commander Xie

313
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:26,520
will also help us

314
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:28,120
enrich the team according to

315
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:29,840
the standards of the New Fourth Army.

316
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,440
Organization, propaganda,

317
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,920
and civilian movements are all short of hands,

318
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:37,180
especially comrades who understand civilian movements.

319
00:15:39,800 --> 00:15:41,200
Whether you agree or not,

320
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,560
I have a condition.

321
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:46,160
You are begging me to go,

322
00:15:46,560 --> 00:15:47,800
yet you're giving me a condition?

323
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:48,720
Yes.

324
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:51,450
If you have a problem with me

325
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:54,080
or you're not happy with your work,

326
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,880
you can tell me directly.

327
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:58,140
Don't just leave a letter and disappear.

328
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,840
I haven't said I'm going.

329
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,440
You can think about it again.

330
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:04,480
I don't need an answer today.

331
00:16:08,560 --> 00:16:11,240
It's getting late. I'll head back first.

332
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:16,280
Did you come over just to tell me this?

333
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:21,260
I just wanted to make it clear.

334
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:25,400
Recently, the "mopping-up" operation has been tight.

335
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:28,000
Our Civilian Movement Group has to help the organs transfer.

336
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,480
I can't leave at this time.

337
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,440
Of course.

338
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:33,620
You finish the work at hand first.

339
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:36,000
After a while, I'll submit an application to the leaders.

340
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
If it's approved,

341
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,530
I'll take the transfer order and find you.

342
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:44,000
I'll wait for you.

343
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,280
Umbrella.

344
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:00,160
Yujiao,

345
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:01,480
that Jianghu Trading Company

346
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,240
that Wanfu is in,

347
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,400
did you go there?

348
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:05,839
Not yet.

349
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:08,720
The agents from Chongqing

350
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,800
and West Shanghai

351
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:12,480
are killing each other,

352
00:17:12,560 --> 00:17:13,680
an eye for an eye.

353
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:14,810
It's a fierce fight.

354
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:18,520
The low-level agents are in a bloodbath every day.

355
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:20,200
They would never dream that

356
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:21,800
their immediate superiors,

357
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,079
those high-level agents,

358
00:17:23,079 --> 00:17:24,359
are actually sitting together,

359
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:26,680
drinking foreign liquor, smoking cigars,

360
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,960
and talking happily while

361
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,760
making a fortune.

362
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:32,120
This is the so-called

363
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:34,850
"tight at the front, gorging at the rear."

364
00:17:35,120 --> 00:17:36,440
Those who occupy high positions

365
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:38,200
only recognize money.

366
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:40,760
Do you know

367
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:41,680
what tight commodities

368
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:42,880
they are exchanging?

369
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:46,160
Salt, grain, cloth,

370
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,760
tung oil, bristles,

371
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,520
to medicine and foreign goods.

372
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:50,720
Which one isn't an embargoed item

373
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,000
between the occupied area

374
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,280
and the KMT-controlled area?

375
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,880
When Wanfu told me this,

376
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:57,120
I found it extremely absurd.

377
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:59,680
Wanfu acts as a puppet for these devils.

378
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:01,360
He's very depressed.

379
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:02,280
But

380
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:03,900
his current position,

381
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:06,040
including the passes he holds,

382
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:09,720
are crucial to us.

383
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:12,540
I understand that too.

384
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:15,000
I was also thinking about

385
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,880
how to persuade Wanfu

386
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:19,970
to help us raise supplies for the New Fourth Army.

387
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:23,760
Mrs. Ding, canned food.

388
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:24,360
Thank you.

389
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:31,240
Hasn't the organization given us

390
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:33,860
new tasks for supplies and transportation?

391
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:34,740
I was thinking,

392
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:37,160
if we really use Jianghu Trading

393
00:18:37,360 --> 00:18:38,440
as a platform,

394
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,960
it will definitely be more convenient

395
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,320
and safer.

396
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:45,320
Have you figured out how to tell him?

397
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:49,400
No.

398
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,600
I don't want to lie to him,

399
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,320
but I'm worried that

400
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:07,960
if he refuses,

401
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:10,320
we'll lose all our chances.

402
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:14,800
We really can't rush this.

403
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:17,640
I think we need to observe more of

404
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:18,720
his working state

405
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:20,650
and his ideological dynamics.

406
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:22,240
It's best if we find

407
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:24,520
the most appropriate and natural timing

408
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:26,320
to win him over little by little.

409
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:33,980
How is Master's health recently?

410
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:37,400
Master just lives in his own world.

411
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,280
In his world,

412
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:44,920
our troops are winning battles every day

413
00:19:45,320 --> 00:19:47,680
and recovering lost territories every day.

414
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:49,000
It's just that Master's eyes are bad

415
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,800
and he can't read the newspaper.

416
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:53,240
Wanfu and I read the newspaper every day

417
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,930
and make up stories for him.

418
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:56,080
Wanfu also said

419
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,240
he wanted to live in Master's

420
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,600
world too.

421
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:01,080
That day,

422
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:04,400
Wanfu told me that lie

423
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,640
again.

424
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,840
We laughed as we talked.

425
00:20:10,360 --> 00:20:11,920
And then we cried

426
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:14,760
as we laughed.

427
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:23,600
The victory Master wants

428
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,520
will come one day.

429
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:30,730
It definitely will.

430
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:33,160
Yueming.

431
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,600
Wanfu's dad's job

432
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:37,560
is dealing with devils.

433
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:40,800
He has to pretend to be a profit-driven merchant,

434
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:42,120
between the enemy and the puppet regime,

435
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:43,920
cleverly passing intelligence

436
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:45,840
and transferring crucial supplies.

437
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:47,960
In front of traitors and intelligence agents,

438
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:49,960
he cannot show the slightest flaw.

439
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:53,800
Meanwhile, on a different battlefield,

440
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:55,680
equally terrifying is

441
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:59,610
Yunkui's father returning from Central Jiangsu to Haiwen.

442
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:01,720
The Self-defense Group he leads

443
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,400
is under the leadership of the New Fourth Army,

444
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:06,060
but cannot use the banner of the New Fourth Army.

445
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:09,360
It must take root behind enemy lines with a grey appearance

446
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:12,200
to win over more anti-Japanese forces.

447
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:17,720
I say, is the harvest from this trip to Central Jiangsu great?

448
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:19,920
Yes, it is.

449
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:20,850
That's good.

450
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:24,410
Then we can be considered the New Fourth Army, right?

451
00:21:24,600 --> 00:21:25,480
Externally,

452
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:27,640
we don't use the banner of the New Fourth Army,

453
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:29,600
but manage our Haiwen Self-Defense Group well

454
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:31,130
to let Yutang Pier serve us.

455
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:32,000
Why is that?

456
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:34,570
The pier is our biggest advantage.

457
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:35,920
Although the land routes are blocked,

458
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:36,720
the waterways

459
00:21:36,840 --> 00:21:38,160
are still viable for us.

460
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:40,920
There are also many Japanese sentries on the water.

461
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:43,440
Yes, the Yangtze River is sealed up tight.

462
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:45,500
Just keep up the disguise.

463
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:47,120
We all still have to do business, don't we?

464
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:49,240
Our next task is

465
00:21:49,520 --> 00:21:51,320
to eliminate the bandit forces from all sides.

466
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:52,200
And on the docks,

467
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,600
we can't let them set up checkpoints arbitrarily

468
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:54,800
and collect taxes randomly anymore.

469
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:55,640
We need to keep up our disguise

470
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:58,500
to provide better supplies for the New Fourth Army.

471
00:21:58,560 --> 00:22:00,480
The main concern is that the Japanese

472
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:02,010
often come to make trouble.

473
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:04,120
Then we should show off the prestige

474
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,320
of our Self-defense Group.

475
00:22:05,320 --> 00:22:05,920
Right?

476
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:06,480
Fight.

477
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:07,360
Not only fight,

478
00:22:07,360 --> 00:22:09,000
but we also need to work with nearby towns

479
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:09,840
to coordinate well

480
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:11,500
and keep each other informed.

481
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:15,000
Some newly appointed puppet town heads and heads of a bao,

482
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,920
they just brush us off on the surface.

483
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:18,920
Secretly, they collude with the Japanese

484
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:19,850
and inform on us.

485
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:22,000
Those who were fighting as guerrillas in the village,

486
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:24,130
the wounded New Fourth Army soldiers,

487
00:22:24,320 --> 00:22:26,320
were all captured and buried alive.

488
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:27,840
Even the civilians who protected them

489
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:28,900
suffered greatly.

490
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:30,480
The guerrillas had to withdraw.

491
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:32,720
The whole village has become deeply puppetized.

492
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:35,000
Other villages are in the same situation.

493
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:37,040
The most hateful are these two-faced people,

494
00:22:37,040 --> 00:22:38,280
who are also very cunning.

495
00:22:38,280 --> 00:22:39,720
They should all be shot.

496
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:42,120
We still need to treat them differently.

497
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:45,040
For those bad people who betray their fellow villagers,

498
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:46,680
let the Pistol Squad severely punish them

499
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,140
to make an example of them.

500
00:22:48,360 --> 00:22:49,000
As for some people,

501
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,040
I believe they have a conscience.

502
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,120
It's just because they are too afraid

503
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:55,120
that they have to serve the Japanese.

504
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:57,240
So, after the Japanese Army's mopping-up operations,

505
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,600
they will definitely withdraw.

506
00:22:58,600 --> 00:22:59,760
For these two-faced people,

507
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:00,920
we must protect them well

508
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:01,980
and embolden them.

509
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,170
At the same time,

510
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:07,040
we need to handle our relationships with the gangs well.

511
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:09,040
Using the power of gangs to control gangs

512
00:23:09,040 --> 00:23:11,120
can yield twice the result with half the effort.

513
00:23:11,120 --> 00:23:12,980
Once these people drink too much,

514
00:23:13,360 --> 00:23:15,080
they exchange cards and become sworn brothers,

515
00:23:15,080 --> 00:23:17,010
their heads full of Guan Yunchang.

516
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:18,720
Why do you care about Guan Yunchang?

517
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:19,680
What our Self-defense Group needs to win over

518
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,520
is the middle force.

519
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:22,440
As long as they are anti-Japanese at heart,

520
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,700
we can all be brothers.

521
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,170
Makes sense.

522
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:27,240
Understood.

523
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:31,760
Freshly made meat pies, hot meat pies.

524
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:33,160
Give me a meat pie.

525
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,240
Sure.

526
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,080
Two pies.

527
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:41,680
Meat pies, hot meat pies.

528
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:43,920
Sir, would you like a pie?

529
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:45,160
Give me one.

530
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:46,440
Sure.

531
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,200
Here is your pie.

532
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:55,800
Take care.

533
00:23:58,680 --> 00:24:00,600
Meat pies, hot meat pies.

534
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:02,880
Congratulations, sir.

535
00:24:03,760 --> 00:24:06,680
I will give you three phrases free of charge.

536
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:19,920
How are you still alive, you maggot?

537
00:24:20,840 --> 00:24:22,280
I must go to Jianghu Commerce

538
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:24,840
to meet you, Manager He Bishi.

539
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,340
This is really something.

540
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:31,840
After all that, we meet again.

541
00:24:32,320 --> 00:24:32,960
Alright.

542
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,840
Since your superiors sent you

543
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:36,100
to do business with me,

544
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:38,160
I will do my best.

545
00:24:38,760 --> 00:24:41,360
Seeing you here feels like a dream.

546
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:43,680
I'm the one who feels like dreaming.

547
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:45,840
Never in my life did I dream

548
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,090
that I would become what I am today.

549
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,680
I never dreamed

550
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:52,600
I'd be doing such big business every day,

551
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:55,260
even bigger than Mr. Tian's business back then.

552
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:57,940
This is a ship of goods for the Fifth War Area.

553
00:24:58,160 --> 00:25:00,620
Deliver it to Wusongkou as soon as possible.

554
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,240
As for the pass and the payment,

555
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:08,240
just have your men

556
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:10,800
deliver the goods to our West Shanghai warehouse.

557
00:25:10,800 --> 00:25:12,400
I am now directly under Chongqing.

558
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,880
Contact me directly if anything comes up.

559
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,040
Alright, got it.

560
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:21,560
For making you and Master suffer so much,

561
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:23,920
I am sorry.

562
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:43,800
Blindy,

563
00:25:44,040 --> 00:25:44,520
do you still remember

564
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:45,760
how we met?

565
00:25:46,360 --> 00:25:48,400
After you told my fortune that year,

566
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:50,320
the two of us

567
00:25:50,320 --> 00:25:51,560
were tied together.

568
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:53,490
For all these years,

569
00:25:53,840 --> 00:25:56,170
we've crawled out of piles of dead bodies.

570
00:25:56,760 --> 00:25:58,020
Fighting the Japanese

571
00:25:58,760 --> 00:25:59,880
to the very end.

572
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,000
Live well.

573
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,960
You've grown up.

574
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:09,200
You too.

575
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,160
On August 16th,

576
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:26,600
after learning that the Japanese army had retreated,

577
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:29,740
the Military Commission ordered the Ninth War Area

578
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:32,160
to immediately start a pursuit

579
00:26:33,040 --> 00:26:35,700
and look for an opportunity to recover Yueyang.

580
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:40,400
The 99th Army immediately went towards Xinshi

581
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:41,960
to track and pursue.

582
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:43,280
Good.

583
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:50,360
The 34th Division of the Japanese Army

584
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:52,800
attacked the northern Jiangxi area

585
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:56,720
and was repelled by our 30th Group Army.

586
00:26:57,160 --> 00:27:00,020
Both sides retreated to their original positions.

587
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,440
Keep reading.

588
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:08,920
Right away.

589
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,380
You have some water first.

590
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:23,520
Read.

591
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,240
I'm reading.

592
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:28,760
The 34th Division of the Japanese Army

593
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:30,960
attacked the northern Jiangxi area

594
00:27:31,080 --> 00:27:32,240
and was repelled by our 30th...

595
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,240
No, no, no.

596
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,240
You just read this.

597
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:36,880
Really? I read it?

598
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:39,240
Master, my eyes are blurry.

599
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:40,240
Let me take a rest.

600
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:40,720
Let me take a rest.

601
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:42,320
Let me pour you some water, Father.

602
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:43,320
Come.

603
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,920
Master, I'll continue reading.

604
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:56,040
Wuhan has been recovered.

605
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:01,400
Wuhan has been recovered?

606
00:28:01,600 --> 00:28:02,760
Yes, it says so here.

607
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:04,340
Wuhan has been recovered.

608
00:28:05,080 --> 00:28:06,140
I'll keep reading.

609
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:09,080
The frontline soldiers were unstoppable,

610
00:28:09,320 --> 00:28:11,800
attacked Wuchang from Zhengyang Gate,

611
00:28:12,040 --> 00:28:14,170
and engaged in fierce street battles.

612
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:18,480
The remnants of the Japanese army were at a loss,

613
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:20,480
fleeing in all directions.

614
00:28:21,360 --> 00:28:22,320
Let me see.

615
00:28:22,320 --> 00:28:23,440
Take a look.

616
00:28:24,760 --> 00:28:26,280
Wuhan is recovered... Where?

617
00:28:26,280 --> 00:28:27,200
Right here.

618
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:29,480
Wuhan is recovered today.

619
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:30,760
Wanfu.

620
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:32,480
The food is ready.

621
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:33,720
Okay.

622
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:35,720
Master, I'm going to cook.

623
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,200
Go.

624
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:40,920
Wuhan has been recovered.

625
00:28:42,080 --> 00:28:44,200
China will win!

626
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:45,400
What's wrong with you,

627
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:46,260
China will win!

628
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:47,850
looking so distracted?

629
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:49,040
You forgot to take a slip.

630
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:51,570
The three towns of Wuhan have been recovered.

631
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:53,240
China will win!

632
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,300
I've had something on my mind lately.

633
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:56,920
What is it?

634
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:58,330
I was just thinking,

635
00:28:58,440 --> 00:29:00,440
Lin Changgeng and Liao Fengnian

636
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,920
just treat me as a puppet to issue passes,

637
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,840
and a shield for them to make money.

638
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:07,160
If this continues, something will go wrong sooner or later.

639
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:08,200
I'm thinking...

640
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:12,250
Master is almost fully recovered.

641
00:29:12,520 --> 00:29:13,760
When can we

642
00:29:14,120 --> 00:29:15,920
escape from this den of thieves?

643
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:19,400
Wanfu, I have an idea.

644
00:29:20,040 --> 00:29:21,400
Those passes you have

645
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:24,560
that exempt goods from inspection,

646
00:29:25,040 --> 00:29:26,480
can you give me a few?

647
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,480
Why do you need those?

648
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:33,120
You know I have a small trading firm, right?

649
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:35,080
With the passes,

650
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:37,570
we can make a little more money.

651
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:39,940
When it's time for us to leave,

652
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:42,800
we'll still need money on hand, won't we?

653
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:45,880
Okay, you're so thoughtful.

654
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:48,120
Leave it to me.

655
00:29:51,280 --> 00:29:52,160
Give me the apron.

656
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,290
I'll start cooking.

657
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:57,800
Go accompany Master.

658
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,400
Don't let him keep reading the newspaper,

659
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,520
lest we be exposed.

660
00:30:11,320 --> 00:30:12,180
Coming, Madam.

661
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:13,680
Feel free to look around.

662
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,160
Please wait a moment.

663
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:17,960
Here.

664
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:19,600
Please come again.

665
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:20,000
Okay.

666
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,040
Thank you.

667
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:25,120
Yujiao,

668
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:28,840
has the batch of goods I asked you to order arrived?

669
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:29,760
Yes, it has.

670
00:30:30,840 --> 00:30:31,920
Please go inside first.

671
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:33,240
I'll show you.

672
00:30:36,120 --> 00:30:37,560
This way, please.

673
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:43,320
The supplies are already in the North Shanghai warehouse.

674
00:30:43,320 --> 00:30:45,380
Take a look at this face powder first.

675
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,770
I was just about to tell you.

676
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:49,840
Boss Yu can't make it this time.

677
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:51,720
Why?

678
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:55,520
After the last batch of goods was shipped to Eastern Anhui,

679
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:58,000
it was intercepted by the diehard troops,

680
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:01,320
and a very serious clash broke out between the two sides.

681
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:04,000
To prevent the medicine from being snatched,

682
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:06,440
Boss Yu was seriously injured.

683
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,640
Then what about this batch of goods?

684
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:14,370
Who should we find to escort it?

685
00:31:15,320 --> 00:31:17,180
We can only find a boat in Shanghai

686
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:20,090
and ship it directly to Southern Jiangsu.

687
00:31:23,560 --> 00:31:26,000
Then we need to find someone trustworthy.

688
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:33,700
Now the organization is considering

689
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,800
whether you have the courage

690
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,400
to take over Boss Yu's work

691
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:41,840
and take charge of escorting this transport line.

692
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,560
Me?

693
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:48,080
Can I?

694
00:31:49,800 --> 00:31:52,000
You have already withstood many tests.

695
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,200
I

696
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:56,040
have also reported in detail to the organization about you,

697
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,360
Zhang Ruxian,

698
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,040
and Wanfu's situation.

699
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:00,720
We all believe in you.

700
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:06,960
This route

701
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,480
is what Boss Yu risked his life

702
00:32:08,480 --> 00:32:09,840
to open up.

703
00:32:12,520 --> 00:32:14,280
I will definitely do my best.

704
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:16,280
But there is one thing,

705
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:19,600
you may need to personally escort the boats

706
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:21,200
to various ports.

707
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:26,440
But you have an elder and a child at home.

708
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:35,760
Wanfu is a man of affection and loyalty.

709
00:32:36,080 --> 00:32:37,540
Leaving the family to him,

710
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,210
he will take good care of it.

711
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:41,240
But, Ms. Zeng,

712
00:32:41,600 --> 00:32:44,240
previously I kept asking Wanfu for the pass.

713
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:46,360
Every time I lied to him,

714
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:48,880
I felt really panicked.

715
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:51,040
He is a trustworthy person.

716
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:52,720
It's been so long,

717
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,440
can I tell him now?

718
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:56,200
Here is the thing.

719
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,360
The current top priority

720
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:03,040
is to help the New Fourth Army buy essential supplies.

721
00:33:04,120 --> 00:33:06,560
So Wanfu's pass is very important.

722
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:10,520
But from your daily descriptions,

723
00:33:10,840 --> 00:33:12,600
Wanfu does not have a comprehensive understanding

724
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:14,040
of our Party's work.

725
00:33:14,360 --> 00:33:15,320
On the contrary,

726
00:33:15,760 --> 00:33:17,820
his distance from the New Fourth Army

727
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,960
can actually protect our work

728
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:23,690
and become the biggest protective umbrella.

729
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:27,920
Okay.

730
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:30,600
I understand.

731
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:35,000
Yueming.

732
00:33:35,280 --> 00:33:36,560
This was the first time Mom

733
00:33:36,560 --> 00:33:38,960
independently carried out a mission assigned by the Party.

734
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:40,920
These supplies had to pass through the enemy's

735
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:42,080
heavy checkpoints

736
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:44,680
and be delivered to the Central Jiangsu Base Area.

737
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:47,440
They were used by the New Fourth Army to fight the Japanese,

738
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:49,200
as precious as blood.

739
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:52,200
Mom completed the mission,

740
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:55,320
but for the sake of secrecy,

741
00:33:55,440 --> 00:33:57,240
she couldn't tell Wanfu's dad.

742
00:33:58,360 --> 00:34:00,620
This also caused his misunderstanding.

743
00:34:03,800 --> 00:34:04,880
I called you out

744
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:08,040
because Master is at home,

745
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,280
and it's not convenient to talk.

746
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,520
I want to tell you two things.

747
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:18,159
Tomorrow, Lin Changgeng wants us

748
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:21,560
to go to Deputy Chief Jin of the Propaganda Department's house for dinner.

749
00:34:21,560 --> 00:34:24,820
I heard this person enters and leaves Wang Jingwei's house

750
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:26,699
without needing to be announced.

751
00:34:27,199 --> 00:34:29,159
Lin Changgeng wants to use Jianghu Trading

752
00:34:29,159 --> 00:34:30,420
to curry favor with him

753
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:31,820
and let him buy shares.

754
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:32,880
Do I have to go too?

755
00:34:33,239 --> 00:34:34,840
Yan Huiru named you.

756
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:37,360
I don't know what she's up to.

757
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:39,880
I'm guessing

758
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,040
if she knows

759
00:34:42,560 --> 00:34:44,440
that you're using Jiyun Trading Company

760
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,960
to get passes from me.

761
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:47,920
Or maybe,

762
00:34:48,679 --> 00:34:51,010
she just wants you there for appearances.

763
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,280
I understand.

764
00:34:54,520 --> 00:34:56,120
What about the second thing?

765
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,840
Lately,

766
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:06,730
you've been acting mysterious and busy all the time.

767
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:09,680
You've asked me for a total of 39 passes.

768
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:11,330
I want to know

769
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,600
who you are working with.

770
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:15,440
What is it?

771
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,610
I'll just ask you directly.

772
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:22,360
Are you working with Zeng Xuefei?

773
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:25,600
Are you working for them?

774
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,120
I guessed it long ago.

775
00:35:30,720 --> 00:35:33,000
Why didn't you tell me the truth?

776
00:35:33,640 --> 00:35:34,640
All these years,

777
00:35:35,720 --> 00:35:38,050
we've overcome so many hurdles together.

778
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:40,760
We have no secrets between us.

779
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,960
You didn't tell me about such a big thing.

780
00:35:43,960 --> 00:35:46,160
Besides, it's not a bad thing.

781
00:35:46,720 --> 00:35:48,160
It's a good thing.

782
00:35:50,440 --> 00:35:51,680
In your hearts,

783
00:35:51,680 --> 00:35:53,160
I'm still that little bug,

784
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:54,360
right?

785
00:35:55,560 --> 00:35:57,960
I'm still the deadwood Master talks about.

786
00:35:58,200 --> 00:35:59,080
Still that

787
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,960
worthless guy.

788
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:05,680
We are still not equal.

789
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:13,440
But you are changing, and so am I.

790
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:15,840
You are growing, and so am I.

791
00:36:16,240 --> 00:36:17,960
You want to walk a clean path,

792
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:20,400
and I do too.

793
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,260
I'm telling you this today

794
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:25,240
because I'm hurt.

795
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:27,680
I'm hurt that you keep everything from me.

796
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:28,920
I'm hurt

797
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:32,100
that we don't even have this little bit of trust.

798
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:35,560
What am I?

799
00:36:38,640 --> 00:36:39,840
I'm nothing.

800
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:43,440
Wanfu.

801
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:46,640
I am growing,

802
00:36:47,680 --> 00:36:49,400
and I see your growth too.

803
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:51,280
You should know

804
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:53,200
the importance of this matter

805
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,770
and how dangerous it is.

806
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:57,560
It shouldn't be told to just anyone.

807
00:36:57,960 --> 00:36:59,840
I haven't grown apart from you.

808
00:37:01,200 --> 00:37:01,960
I also hope

809
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,880
to fight side by side with you.

810
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:07,280
I told Ms. Zeng my thoughts.

811
00:37:07,680 --> 00:37:08,760
Ms. Zeng said

812
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:11,200
I could tell you everything

813
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:13,440
at the right time.

814
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,800
Do you want to hear it now?

815
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:23,360
Yes.

816
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:58,760
How is Fu Fan doing?

817
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:01,040
The bullet hit her shoulder.

818
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:02,560
It was a Type 38 rifle.

819
00:38:02,560 --> 00:38:04,020
It went straight through.

820
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,840
Fortunately, no vital organs were injured.

821
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:07,880
She just finished surgery.

822
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:09,140
She lost a lot of blood,

823
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:11,560
and the wound is infected.

824
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,360
Her high fever persists.

825
00:38:13,560 --> 00:38:14,890
If the fever continues,

826
00:38:16,240 --> 00:38:17,700
she'll be in great danger.

827
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:32,800
You're awake.

828
00:38:35,720 --> 00:38:36,720
Xiaoyue.

829
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,560
What are you looking for, Xiaoyue?

830
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:49,560
Looking for what?

831
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:51,320
My gun.

832
00:38:51,520 --> 00:38:52,440
Gun.

833
00:38:53,200 --> 00:38:54,040
Don't worry,

834
00:38:54,120 --> 00:38:56,040
your gun is kept safe for you.

835
00:38:58,120 --> 00:39:00,520
I was out of bullets.

836
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,720
I don't know

837
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:06,200
if I hit the enemy.

838
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,760
I'm so useless.

839
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:11,440
I'm not willing to die like this.

840
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,800
Don't talk nonsense.

841
00:39:13,200 --> 00:39:15,400
You'll be fine once the fever breaks.

842
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:17,120
Rest well.

843
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:24,040
I thought

844
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:29,360
I would never see you again.

845
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:31,200
Well, here I am.

846
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,120
You said

847
00:39:40,080 --> 00:39:42,680
the uniform is your coffin.

848
00:39:44,560 --> 00:39:45,760
Once you put it on,

849
00:39:47,080 --> 00:39:49,340
you must be ready to sacrifice yourself,

850
00:39:50,160 --> 00:39:53,600
without fear and without giving up.

851
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:57,040
I am wearing a uniform now too.

852
00:39:58,160 --> 00:40:00,080
And I won't give up either.

853
00:40:03,520 --> 00:40:04,850
Focus on your recovery.

854
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,560
When you get better,

855
00:40:09,640 --> 00:40:11,170
I'll wait for you in Haiwen.

856
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:13,650
For the rest of the journey,

857
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:16,560
we will walk together.

858
00:40:17,760 --> 00:40:19,200
I'll be by your side.

859
00:40:33,600 --> 00:40:34,400
How is it?

860
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:37,250
Her temperature has finally dropped.

861
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,160
It's fine now.

862
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:40,360
Xiaoyue, you're fine now.

863
00:40:43,440 --> 00:40:45,280
I have a silver tongue too.

864
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:47,200
Give me the thermometer.

865
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:50,360
I'll chew it right up.

866
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:51,560
Okay.

867
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:56,420
What you just said,

868
00:40:56,520 --> 00:40:58,120
we all heard it.

869
00:41:06,080 --> 00:41:07,720
Please be our witnesses.

870
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:13,400
Fu Fan and I

871
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:15,960
will definitely be your witnesses.

872
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:18,610
But Xiaoyue, you have to promise me

873
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:20,280
to recover well.

874
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:21,940
Once you're fully healed,

875
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,620
we'll send you back to Haiwen.

876
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:25,600
But when that time comes,

877
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:27,640
you and Yunkui

878
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:29,680
must invite us to your wedding.

879
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:39,320
Xiaoyue.

880
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:39,970
Xiaoyue.

881
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:40,760
Xiaoyue.

882
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:41,960
Xiaoyue.

883
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,850
It's nothing. She's just too weak.

884
00:41:45,960 --> 00:41:47,420
Let her get some good rest.

885
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:56,480
Wang.

886
00:41:58,880 --> 00:41:59,800
Thank you.

887
00:42:42,320 --> 00:42:43,600
I remember

888
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:46,320
a poem

889
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:49,360
that you used to recite.

890
00:42:50,680 --> 00:42:52,800
The clouds

891
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:57,760
and moon in it

892
00:43:01,040 --> 00:43:04,080
must refer to the two of us.
